c: 2
v: 91
t: "And when it is said to them, \"Be graced with belief in what Allah has revealed,\" they say, \"We only accept that which has been handed over to us.\" And they deny that which comes after it, though it is the Truth confirming the authentic that is with them. Say, \"Why then did you oppose and slay the Prophets of Allah, if you were indeed believers (in the earlier Revelations)"